title: Speak Chinese: Volume 1-2
description:
Speak Chinese: Volume 1-2

2 Audio CDs: Chinese: MP3, 128 Kbps (2 channels) | Duration: 2 Hours | 2008 | 

ISBN-10: 7561920652, 7561920660

2 PDF Books

Overal size: 279 MB | Genre: Learning Chinese | Level: Pre-Intermediate

Volume 1 of Speaking Chinese (3rd Edition) has altogether 20 lessons in 8 units covering topics such as Work, Sports, Transportation, Literature and Art, Chinese and Chinese Characters, Telephone and Internet, Weather, and Travel.

Volume 2 of Speaking Chinese (3rd Edition) has altogether 20 lessons in 7 units covering topics such as Chinese Customs, Marriage, Architecture in Beijing, Visiting Someone, Education, Local Flavor, Visits
